{"tid":1893112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「全港社區抗疫連線」18區今設400個服務點派發合共100萬個口罩 總召集人為港區人大代表陳振彬！","createTime":"2020-02-23T04:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T16:29:19.000Z","uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4236a35209664a062d3e552cde10a309f0b8a32b","tid":1893112,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceebb70481b777062f3b3d03c8b8a028753bede4","tid":1893112,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:31:04.000Z","msg":"「全港社區抗疫連線」早上11時起，在全港18區400個服務點免費派發合共100萬個口罩，又開通網上登記系統，派發10萬個口罩。其中在小西灣街市門口，今早有數十名長者排隊等待派籌。<br />\n<br />\n「全港社區抗疫連線」總召集人、港區人大代表陳振彬說，通過多名善長捐款，成功從全球採購口罩，來源地包括俄羅斯、巴西和印尼等地，會不分政見顔色派口罩，支援有需要的長者、弱勢社群和前線工作人員。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否較政府派口罩的方法更有效率，陳振彬表示，雙方都有各自派口罩的渠道，最重要是共同出一分力。<br />\n<br />\n出席活動的包括行政會議成員葉劉淑儀和張國鈞、工聯會會長吳秋北、以及食物及衞生局前局長高永文等人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510252-20200223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510252-20200223.htm&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyhTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=92f8bda0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510252-20200223.htm&h=63e92da6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510252-20200223.htm</a>"},{"pid":"030f7fd0e0d4e9332b72a60b109de48bd2412930","tid":1893112,"uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KVfUgFJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVfUgFJ.png&h=67a59b59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qsa1F7q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQsa1F7q.png&h=7604792e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRdiJkM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRdiJkM.png&h=3780b370&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xMdCess.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxMdCess.png&h=b3756eae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EX36Sd8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEX36Sd8.png&h=185c01c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47af5330ff9df0b920de5aeb5556a7387841f2f7","tid":1893112,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:38:43.000Z","msg":"用個0.01口罩就換到地址番黎<br />\n除笨有精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdebaab928e04462adafb9a372651462364cd0d3","tid":1893112,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:54:15.000Z","msg":"車厘車厘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b139b7132ea9aca9cbb0e93ffae5ef36baaf14","tid":1893112,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:56:26.000Z","msg":"拎咁多資料派五個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11a7bcdca4e10cca55bd52f2b952186079ee7d0","tid":1893112,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9b139b7132ea9aca9cbb0e93ffae5ef36baaf14","tid":1893112,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:56:26.000Z","msg":"拎咁多資料派五個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:57:25.000Z","msg":"啲廢老唔識, 會照比哂<br />\n之後就會有「社區主任」黎關心佢<br />\n九月會叫佢投禮義廉"},{"pid":"80827743bacd8b3e1b36d6dfc312baa88cdf3407","tid":1893112,"uid":11663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:58:53.000Z","msg":"點解要住址證明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f686660a7826d265e36814cdc24d25169c4ee11","tid":1893112,"uid":204948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:45:38.000Z","msg":"無車厘龜既<img s